name: HonoluluBusArrivals
0:
”alexa start honolulu bus arrivals”
”alexa ask honolulu bus arrivals when will the next bus arrive at stop 131”
”alexa ask honolulu bus arrivals when will the next route 1 arrive at stop 131”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: honolulu bus arrivals
des: This skill allows for a user to obtain arrival times for buses at specified stops in the City and County of Honolulu. You will need to know the ID number of the stop you want to obtain arrival time for. Not affiliated with Oahu Transit Services, the City and County of Honolulu, or the Hawaii State Department of Transportation.
